      "src": null,
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "\n        <p>\"Dr. Cuca's\" chop shop hides beneath <strong>MindSound Music</strong>, a legit-enough store fronting a warren of cover businesses — a cheap-electronics outlet, an Amazonian café. The body shop sits below, screened behind layers of misdirection and a fast-talking receptionist who runs surveillance on everyone who walks in.</p>"
      },
      "system": {},
      "sort": 0,
      "ownership": {
        "default": -1
      },
