    {
      "_id": "3bc15556d422b713",
      "name": "Hooks & Behind the Scenes",
      "type": "text",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "video": {
        "controls": true,
        "volume": 0.5
      },
      "src": null,
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "\n        <p><strong>Hooks.</strong> The store runs on several layers of deceit. Following the cyberdoc thread (legally or not) eventually exposes the hidden clinic.</p>\n        <p><strong>Behind the Scenes.</strong> \"Dr. Cuca\" is <strong>Lindy</strong>, a Renraku covert operative who screens the desperate before admitting \"patients.\" The chop shop is a front for Renraku's underground program testing illegal <strong>behavioural-control cyberware</strong> — the gang's edge, and what compromised Tanner. Lindy is bright and not easily fooled.</p>"
      },
      "system": {},
      "sort": 0,
      "ownership": {
        "default": -1
      },
      "flags": {},
      "_stats": {
